{"tid":118064,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"科學修正癌細胞，微軟承諾在十年內解決癌症","createTime":"2017-02-12T17:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T15:13:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6ad4b74030bf90597caa6a709e57c6231461ef","tid":118064,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"王瑾瑜 05/10/2016<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87-678x381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E7%2599%258C%25E7%2597%2587-678x381.jpg&h=033c9801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微軟科學家認為，電腦科學與生物學擁有非常深厚的聯繫 （圖：Ed Miller）<br />\n微軟（Microsoft）承諾將運用突破性電腦科技，破解疾病的細胞密碼，重新編製它們返回健康狀態，並希望在 10 年內「解決癌症的問題」。這著名科技公司目前已經組建了一支由世界最優秀的生物學家、程式編寫員和工程師組成的隊伍，將會像修正電腦系統中的程式錯誤一樣解決癌症。<br />\n<br />\n劍橋大學生物學副教授雅斯敏&middot;菲莎（Jasmin Fisher）博士認為，我們必須利用科技理解癌症，明白健康細胞變成癌細胞背後的生理過程，然後找出處理這問題的方法。而她選用的研究方法非常特別，利用電腦科學的角度觀看癌症，嘗試理解細胞運作背後的「程式」。"},{"pid":"7e18a21483d3621626b50e43a4f4bc5e9b01c83f","tid":118064,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7c18dfce8aec3626105130e593731aea337920","tid":118064,"uid":5865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:41:11.000Z","msg":"死火 準備成身bugs<br />\n（然後訓隔壁病床果個叫你轉Linux）"},{"pid":"17ba4327d36cedd7774273c06b81fd1514930888","tid":118064,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:43:12.000Z","msg":"癌症細胞搞到<br />\n細胞衰老仲會遠嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4653035ba2e68bffd3a8448fb2a5bc8f35f2d9","tid":118064,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:51:24.0